<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Rothenburg ob der Tauber</head><p>Der Rat teilt sein Bedauern wegen des Streits mit dem Viztum und anderen mit und bietet Vermittlung an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_360" id="179v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_360_r1l11"><expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_360_r1l12"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / vmb ſölich cʒwıtracht vnd veintſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l13">als Jr habt mit dem vıcʒtum vnd <expan>ettlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l14">Das ıſt vns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> nicht lıeb ſunder in gancʒen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l15">trewen leıde / . vnd künden wir mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> botſcheften </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l16"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ſüſt ıht gütes dar cʒü gereden <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> getün / . das ſıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l17">cʒü frewntſchaft cʒüge / des <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir vns nicht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>drıeſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l18">laſſen / . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewr <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr vns ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l19"><expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> da </del> / <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> <expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> brıefe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l20">bey <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ob ew ıh cʒe </del> <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan> es ew cʒeſynne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l21">daʒ wir ıht darcʒü tün <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . 
<del rend="strikethrough">was vvir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> getün <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l22">
<del rend="strikethrough">Das </del> So <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir das <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> verſüchen vnd vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l23"> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>mügen</expan> vnd peſtes 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>g<ex>er</ex></expan></del> darynne tün / . wan vvo wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l24">ew etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_360" id="179v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, umb sölich czwitracht und
                        veintschaft als ir habt mit dem vicztum und
                            <expan>ettlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, das ist uns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> nicht lieb, sunder in ganczen trewen leide;
                        und künden wir mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> botscheften
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> süst iht gütes dar czü gereden
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> getün, das sich czü frewntschaft czüge,
                        des <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir uns nicht
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>driesse<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen.
                                <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewr <expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir uns ewr <expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet an <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        briefe bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan> es ew czesynne, daz wir iht darczü tün
                                <expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir das <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> versüchen und unser
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>mügen</expan> und pestes darynne tün. Wan wo wir
                        ew etc.</ab>
</div>
